<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhōng guó de zǎo chén wǔ diǎn zhōng, chuán lái qí dǎo shēng.
 qiú shén dài lái fù xìng hé píng, cì xià hé yī dé shèng.
 zhōng guó de zǎo chén wǔ diǎn zhōng, chuán lái jìng bài shēng.
 rén rén dōu xiàn chū zhēn chéng de ài, wǔ hú sì hǎi jiē dì xiōng.
 zhōng guó de zǎo chén wǔ diǎn zhōng, chuán lái qí dǎo shēng.
 fēi yuè le wàn shuǐ qiān shān róng huà bīng lěng de xīn líng.
 zài méi yǒu kǔn suǒ, zài méi yǒu zhàn zhēng,
 dài lái le zhù fú, niǔ zhuǎn le mìng yùn, jīn nián shì hǎo shōu chéng.</lyrics>
<title>zhōng guó de zǎo chén wǔ diǎn zhōng 迦南268</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
